T1  - What did structural adjustment adjust?: The association of policies and growth with repeated IMF and World Bank adjustment loans
AU  - Easterly, William
JO  - Journal of Development Economics
VL  - 76
IS  - 1
SP  - 1
EP  - 22
PY  - 2005
DA  - 2005/02/01/
SN  - 0304-3878
